limited service.

01:09.536 --> 01:15.008 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the glitch also delayed more
than 1,000
flights, and left passengers
stranded.

01:15.042 --> 01:17.377 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
