but now I
got a flight tomorrow.

01:32.025 --> 01:34.528 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, it was the fact that they
didn't let me
know what was going on.

01:34.561 --> 01:37.831 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
