buildings and tore
through concrete walls on
Saturday.

04:59.399 --> 05:04.004 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Soldiers and first-responders
worked Sunday
to clear debris caked in mud.

05:04.037 --> 05:09.543 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Wal-Mart is
moving to muscle
up in online sales, buying
online retailer

05:09.576 --> 05:11.211 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
