points, and the
S&amp;P 500 slipped two.

05:36.703 --> 05:43.076 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And Russia fired
back today,
after its entire Paralympic team
was banned

05:43.109 --> 05:46.846 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
