refugees' unseen

06:15.475 --> 06:20.280 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
needs; and much more.

06:20.313 --> 06:32.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: The two major
candidates for president
jostled for position in the last
week, stepping

06:32.959 --> 06:38.898 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
