Candidate:
These reforms will offer biggest
tax revolution

06:48.541 --> 06:51.211 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
since the Reagan tax reform.

06:51.244 --> 06:56.650 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Trump chose the
traditional campaign
setting of the Detroit Economic
Club to deliver

06:56.683 --> 07:00.720 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
