economic ideas, starting
with taxes.

07:00.754 --> 07:06.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: I am proposing an
across-the-board
income tax reduction, especially
for middle-income

07:06.960 --> 07:08.295 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Americans.

07:08.328 --> 07:12.899 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
