nation to compete.

07:24.010 --> 07:29.516 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: But throughout his
scripted remarks,
Trump was regularly interrupted
at least a

07:29.549 --> 07:31.584 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
