people had
far more energy and spirit.

07:38.925 --> 07:44.497 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Trump's tax plan
envisions three
income tax brackets of 33
percent, 25 percent

07:44.531 --> 07:46.232 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
