called for a freeze
on new government regulation.

08:02.949 --> 08:08.421 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: It is time to
remove the anchor
dragging us down.

08:08.455 --> 08:09.589 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
