a temporary
moratorium on new agency
regulations.

08:19.799 --> 08:25.038 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Trump said the
specifics of his
plan will be spelled out on his
Web site at

08:25.071 --> 08:26.906 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
