to do damage control.

08:41.554 --> 08:46.860 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Clinton, who
campaigned in Florida
today, including a brewery tour
in St. Petersburg,

08:46.893 --> 08:49.295 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
