09:07.947 --> 09:12.852 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: The candidates
sparred as Trump
tumbled in the polls after a
series of political

09:12.886 --> 09:14.821 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
