launching his own
independent bid for president.

09:33.206 --> 09:34.641 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Are the polls real?

09:34.674 --> 09:36.409 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Will the reset take?

09:36.443 --> 09:41.314 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
