Political Report
and Tamara Keith of NPR.

09:46.019 --> 09:47.187 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Welcome back, ladies.

09:47.220 --> 09:50.056 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
