Radio: Or was
the last one the pivot?

09:53.359 --> 09:55.061 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Or was the last one?

09:55.094 --> 09:57.864 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: Or was the last
