month, we
get one of these teleprompter
speeches.

10:22.422 --> 10:24.357 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
In some way, this was a reset.

10:24.390 --> 10:29.963 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
