traumatized by war.

56:26.416 --> 56:28.252 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A critical report by local
leaders that examined
the area's safety net found that
health care

56:28.285 --> 56:29.987 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
