56:32.256 --> 56:34.124 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Kowsar Ali, a Somali and Arabic
interpreter,
says just figuring out how to
explain a patient's

56:34.157 --> 56:35.392 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
