depression that
are unfamiliar.

56:37.294 --> 56:39.029 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KOWSAR ALI, Jericho Road: It's
actually hard
for them because there's nothing
as depression.

56:39.062 --> 56:40.864 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
