existed in
my country. There's nothing as
depression.

56:40.897 --> 56:41.531 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Dr. Glick says the
initial relief
refugees feel when they reach
safety often

56:41.565 --> 56:43.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
