communicate.

57:01.785 --> 57:03.520 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: So many refugees
have moved
here that the population of Erie
County, home

57:03.553 --> 57:05.355 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
