57:19.636 --> 57:21.505 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. KIM GRISWOLD, Western New
York Center
for Survivors of Torture: Some
of the folks

57:21.538 --> 57:23.073 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
