kids and family.

57:50.200 --> 57:51.902 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: The recent spate
of violent
attacks worldwide have fueled
anti-immigrant

57:51.935 --> 57:53.370 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
